2016-03-03 Nicolas Normand <nnormand@justcodeit.org>
	* cppmt::Opts: can set a suffix message for generated help.
2014-07-11 Nicolas Normand <nnormand@justcodeit.org>
	* Version 0.2.0
	* cppmt::Sqlite: Forbid copy constructor and operator= for class Sqlite.
	* cppmt::Sqlite: Exception will show query.
2014-10-03 Nicolas Normand <nnormand@justcodeit.org>
	* cppmt::Opts: can choose behavior when opening configuration file fails (report error, ignore error or direct exit).
	* cppmt::Opts: can choose option (long and short) names for help and version, as well as help strings.
	* cppmt::Opts: can set a prefix message for generated help.
	* cppmt::Opts: [fix] fixed help message for generated help, for optional arguments (writes '[=<ARG>]' instead of '=[<ARG>]').

2014-10-02 Nicolas Normand <nnormand@justcodeit.org>
	* cppmt::Opts: support for short options in configuration files, support for options without arguments in configuration files.

